    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop your <strong>potatoes</strong> (skins on) into bite sized pieces</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>potatoes</strong> to a baking tray (or two!) with your <strong>dried</strong> <strong>thyme</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>olive</strong> <strong>oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 25-30 min or until golden and crisp</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
