    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>panko</strong> <strong>breadcrumbs</strong> to a plate</p><p>Press the <strong>marinated</strong> <strong>chicken</strong> into the breadcrumbs firmly to evenly coat all over – this is your <strong>breaded chicken</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
